WEBVTT

1
00:07:31.159 --> 00:07:34.162
That beat really sucks.

2
00:07:35.663 --> 00:07:36.581
Is it going well?

3
00:07:37.790 --> 00:07:40.501
Well. it's going.
I still have to mess with it.

4
00:07:42.378 --> 00:07:45.673
You've been down at the studio
a lot lately.

5
00:07:46.299 --> 00:07:50.094
Are you avoiding someone?

6
00:07:51.804 --> 00:07:53.598
I'm not avoiding Kitty.

7
00:07:53.681 --> 00:07:55.850
She's doing her thing and I'm doing mine.

8
00:07:55.933 --> 00:07:58.519
Wouldn't it be better if you two talked?

9
00:08:00.229 --> 00:08:05.026
I don't know.
I just need to make music right now.

10
00:08:05.109 --> 00:08:07.153
I'm not sure it’s going well.

11
00:08:07.737 --> 00:08:08.988
Hey.

12
00:08:09.071 --> 00:08:10.907
You know what you need right now?

13
00:08:13.784 --> 00:08:16.787
Yuri needs music for Seoul Fashion Week.

14
00:08:17.580 --> 00:08:18.915
in two days.

15
00:08:18.998 --> 00:08:20.666
You want to give it a try?

16
00:08:20.750 --> 00:08:21.667
Me?

17
00:08:24.420 --> 00:08:26.214
I don't know if I…

18
00:08:26.297 --> 00:08:30.259
No… You can do it. Absolutely.

19
00:08:30.968 --> 00:08:32.053
You…

20
00:08:32.720 --> 00:08:34.931
you reinvented yourself.

21
00:08:36.390 --> 00:08:37.767
It's the same for Yuri.

22
00:08:42.146 --> 00:08:43.856
I'll do it.

23
00:08:44.357 --> 00:08:46.275
Yuri will really appreciate it.

24
00:08:47.527 --> 00:08:48.694
Do your thing.

25
00:08:48.778 --> 00:08:49.779
All right.

26
00:17:05.941 --> 00:17:07.067
File's all done.

27
00:17:09.069 --> 00:17:12.114
- Do you like it?
- I don't know.

28
00:17:12.990 --> 00:17:14.658
I just hope Yuri likes it.

29
00:17:17.119 --> 00:17:19.413
Then. let's go play it for them.

30
00:17:23.167 --> 00:17:25.252
Who's them? What are you talking about?

31
00:17:25.335 --> 00:17:27.046
Yuri and her producer.

32
00:23:23.276 --> 00:23:25.487
Wow. Yuri actually pulled this off.
